column16: Starlin Castro doubles (17) on a line drive to left fielder Ryan Ludwick.   Joe Mather scores.    Anthony Rizzo to 3rd.
Anthony Rizzo singles on a ground ball to right fielder Jay Bruce.   Luis Valbuena scores.    Joe Mather to 3rd.
Joe Mather singles on a soft ground ball to pitcher Todd Redmond.   Luis Valbuena to 3rd.  Joe Mather advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by pitcher Todd Redmond.
Brooks Raley lines out to shortstop Wilson Valdez.
Adrian Cardenas pops out to third baseman Scott Rolen.
Brett Jackson called out on strikes.
Starlin Castro flies out to left fielder Ryan Ludwick.
Anthony Rizzo flies out to center fielder Drew Stubbs.
Joe Mather grounds out, pitcher Todd Redmond to first baseman Todd Frazier.   Brooks Raley to 3rd.    Luis Valbuena to 2nd.
Luis Valbuena singles on a line drive to right fielder Jay Bruce.   Brooks Raley to 2nd.
Brooks Raley singles on a ground ball to center fielder Drew Stubbs.
Adrian Cardenas pops out to shortstop Wilson Valdez.
Brett Jackson homers (1) on a fly ball to right field.
Steve Clevenger grounds into a force out, second baseman Brandon Phillips to shortstop Wilson Valdez.   Bryan LaHair out at 2nd.
Starlin Castro singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Drew Stubbs.   Luis Valbuena to 3rd.
Joe Mather pops out to catcher Devin Mesoraco in foul territory.
